      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in concours-level condition, having been meticulously maintained to an exacting standard. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a commitment to absolute preservation. Fully inspected and verified to meet our highest benchmarks for mechanical performance and aesthetic integrity, this remains a peerless opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast seeking an as-new experience.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
